=== ANALYSIS: Connect Button Navigation to vault.apideck.com ===
Date: 2025-06-18
Issue: Connect buttons redirect to full page instead of opening dialog/popup

FINDINGS:

1. ROOT CAUSE IDENTIFIED:
   - File: /root/deer-flow/web/src/app/account/IntegrationsTabContent.tsx
   - Lines 181-183: DIRECT NAVIGATION ISSUE
     ```typescript
     // For better UX, let's just redirect in the same window
     // This avoids popup blocker issues
     window.location.href = data.vault_url;
     ```

2. COMPARISON WITH WORKING IMPLEMENTATION:
   - File: /root/deer-flow/web/src/components/deer-flow/integrations-list.tsx
   - Lines 188-209: CORRECT POPUP IMPLEMENTATION
     ```typescript
     const popup = window.open(
       data.vault_url,
       'apideck-vault',
       'width=900,height=700,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes,status=yes,toolbar=no,menubar=no,location=no'
     );
     ```

3. TECHNICAL DETAILS:
   - IntegrationsTabContent.tsx uses window.location.href (causes full page redirect)
   - integrations-list.tsx uses window.open() with popup specifications (correct behavior)
   - Both components have identical backend API calls to /integrations/{service_type}/connect
   - Backend returns vault_url: https://vault.apideck.com/session/{session_token}

4. COMPONENT USAGE LOCATIONS:
   - IntegrationsTabContent.tsx: Used in /root/deer-flow/web/src/app/account/page.tsx
   - integrations-list.tsx: Used in main integrations interface (has correct popup behavior)

5. ADDITIONAL COMPONENTS ANALYZED:
   - integrations-list-static.tsx: Mock implementation (no real connection)
   - integrations-tab.tsx: Mock implementation (no real connection)
   - integrations-dialog.tsx: Dialog wrapper for iframe (unused by problematic component)

SOLUTION REQUIRED:
Replace window.location.href with window.open() popup implementation in IntegrationsTabContent.tsx
to match the working implementation in integrations-list.tsx.

FILES AFFECTED:
- /root/deer-flow/web/src/app/account/IntegrationsTabContent.tsx (PRIMARY ISSUE)
